ve-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141101205926/http://www.projectcasting.com/casting-calls-and-auditions/geostorm-starring-gerard-butler-nasa-scenes-extras-casting-call-in-new-orleans/|archive-date=2014-11-01|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Monday, Jan. 5 Filming Locations for Chicago PD, The Slap, Geostorm, Castle, SVU, & more!|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2015/01/04/monday-jan-5-filming-locations-for-chicago-pd-the-slap-geostorm-castle-svu-more/|accessdate=2015-01-20|publisher=onlocationvacations.com|date=2015-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150108063159/http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2015/01/04/monday-jan-5-filming-locations-for-chicago-pd-the-slap-geostorm-castle-svu-more/|archive-date=2015-01-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。重拍期间{{le|凯瑟琳·温妮克|Katheryn Winnick}}的角色被另一名女演员重新扮演，新角色加入剧本中<ref name=THRGeo>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/jerry-bruckheimer-boards-geostorm-as-866329|title=Warner Bros., Skydance's 'Geostorm' Undergoes Reshoots, Brings on Jerry Bruckheimer|work=The Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=2016-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161217115443/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/jerry-bruckheimer-boards-geostorm-as-866329|archive-date=2016-12-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==發行==
在美國，《氣象戰》原定於2016年3月25日上映<ref>{{cite news|title=Warner Bros Slots ‘Geostorm’ For 2016|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/05/warner-bros-slots-geostorm-for-2016/|accessdate=2014-05-08|newspaper=deadline.com|date=2014-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140507052355/http://www.deadline.com/2014/05/warner-bros-slots-geostorm-for-2016/|archive-date=2014-05-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但於2014年8月，[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]取消了本片的檔期，而改配給《[[蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光|蝙蝠俠對超人：正義曙光]]》<ref>{{cite news|last=Sneider|first=Jeff|title=Warner Bros. Blinks in Marvel Showdown: ‘Batman v Superman’ Avoids ‘Captain America 3'|url=http://www.thewrap.com/warner-bros-blinks-in-marvel-showdown-batman-v-superman-avoids-captain-america-3/|accessdate=2014-08-07|newspaper=thewrap.com|date=2014-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140807180227/http://www.thewrap.com/warner-bros-blinks-in-marvel-showdown-batman-v-superman-avoids-captain-america-3/|archive-date=2014-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年12月11日，華納將《[[叢林之書：起源|叢林之書：起源]]》改於2017年上映，而《氣象戰》則排於2016年10月21日上映<ref name=ReleaseTHR>{{cite news|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|title=Warner Bros. Pushes Release Date of 'Jungle Book: Origins'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/warner-bros-pushes-release-date-756707|accessdate=2014-12-12|publisher=hollywoodreporter.com|date=2014-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150113052625/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/warner-bros-pushes-release-date-756707|archive-date=2015-01-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年9月，華納將本片的上映日改至2017年1月13日<ref>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=Gerard Butler’s ‘Geostorm’ Pushed Back to 2017|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/geostorm-release-date-gerard-butler-2-1201583251/|accessdate=2015-09-04|work=variety.com|date=2015-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150904001601/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/geostorm-release-date-gerard-butler-2-1201583251/|archive-date=2015-09-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年6月，華納又將上映日改定於2017年10月13日<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/06/17/lego-movie-2-delayed-until-2019|title='Lego Movie 2' delayed until 2019|website=Entertainment Weekly's EW.com|access-date=2016-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160619052832/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/06/17/lego-movie-2-delayed-until-2019|archive-date=2016-06-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===評價===
《氣象戰》獲得的評價普遍不佳，主要受到影評人批評電影缺乏令人印象深刻的視覺效果，且角色、劇情和災難場景的表現皆不合格。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據87條評論，持有15%的新鮮度，平均得分3.62／10<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/geostorm |title=Geostorm (2017) |work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=2017-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019221305/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/geostorm |archive-date=2017-10-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，電影獲得了21分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/geostorm |title=Geostorm reviews |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2017-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190118231351/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/geostorm |archive-date=2019-01-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的評價在A+至F間落於「B-」<ref name=opening/>。

===票房===
北美方面，《氣象戰》與《{{le|梅迪亞萬聖節2|Boo 2! A Madea Halloween}}》、《[[雪人_(2017年電影)|雪人]]》、《[[無路可退|無路可退]]》同天上映並競爭，分析師預估《氣象戰》於首週末從3246間戲院中獲得1000萬至1200萬美元的票房<ref name="preview">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/10/geostorm-bomb-boo-2-a-madea-halloween-blade-runner-2049-happy-death-day-box-office-preview-1202190426/|title=Boo 2!’ To Shut Down Expensive ‘Geostorm’ In Crowded Weekend – Box Office Preview|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|date=2017-10-18|accessdate=2017-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171018173133/http://deadline.com/2017/10/geostorm-bomb-boo-2-a-madea-halloween-blade-runner-2049-happy-death-day-box-office-preview-1202190426/|archive-date=2017-10-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國首週末票房達1330萬美元，位居當週票房排名第二<ref name="opening">{{Cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/10/tyler-perry-boo-2-a-madea-halloween-geostorm-bombs-blade-runner-2049-weekend-box-office-1202191950/|title=‘Boo 2! A Madea Halloween’ Reaps $21M+ During October Dumping Ground At The B.O.|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=2017-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171022061209/http://deadline.com/2017/10/tyler-perry-boo-2-a-madea-halloween-geostorm-bombs-blade-runner-2049-weekend-box-office-1202191950/|archive-date=2017-10-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

